The marker used to indicate the start of a matched word inside a snippet
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-output\-format
The format to output the search results in. Either \fB\(dq\fPtext\fB\(dq\fP for plain text or \fB\(dq\fPjson\fB\(dq\fP for JSON output.
.UNINDENT
